{"tid":1831317,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"為抗爭花光盤川 十天沒飯吃","createTime":"2020-01-20T10:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:42:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe51fb9b083486c7e9a0332367cbce0a7177668","tid":1831317,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:04:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200120/GWWZQ2CGKP35MHRBFPKKE6XPEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200120%2FGWWZQ2CGKP35MHRBFPKKE6XPEA%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9yMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=af86f4c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200120%2FGWWZQ2CGKP35MHRBFPKKE6XPEA%2F&h=2e427be7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200120/GWWZQ2CGKP35MHRBFPKKE6XPEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n為抗爭花光盤川 十天沒飯吃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579449044_87db.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579449044_87db.gif&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9yMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=648e267e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579449044_87db.gif</a><br />\n劉鐵民稱綜援收入全部花費在抗爭上，身無分文；幸得有心人贈予飯盒充飢。<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，劉鐵民靠領綜援維持生計，月收約3,900元。他卻選擇將一切使費全花在抗爭上。為了這場抗爭，他已數不清自己餓了多了遍。幸有基層組織向他派發飯券，才不用擔憂三餐溫飽。<br />\n<br />\n「我由1989年六四已花很多錢了，而且那時沒領取綜援，靠執紙皮買食物給大家，那時執紙皮一日可賺百多元，現在不行了，紙皮不值錢，整車只得三至四毫子。」<br />\n<br />\n「我幾乎每天也買，香、打火機、膠紙，甚至有時買箱頭筆給拜祭者寫字，還買了紙張。這些合共花費不少，整個過程3,000多元，幾乎花光（綜援收入）。每個月尾都沒有食物下肚，有時十天沒錢吃飯，有時五天沒錢吃飯。不過，自己犧牲一點也要，別人犧牲性命，我的只是小事。」<br />\n<br />\n手推車是他唯一家當，數十個膠袋裏塞滿的，除了衣物和肥皂、牙膏及洗面巾等日常用品外，就是用來寫貼文宣的剪刀、膠紙及原子筆。這些文具看似不值錢，但對他而言，這些抗爭工具或是貴重財產。不過，他稱曾有跟蹤便衣警員偷去車子。"},{"pid":"0b9abcc34359ca93baadcb2dd711826b9a883806","tid":1831317,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d84812fb7f064ffa2933c4e0e6618f3ccaaeb8a","tid":1831317,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a705c9b1e0bb7382c4f07515703de7a7a8de86","tid":1831317,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2089105cd4c0460cf784cc705b73f75d9f28846c","tid":1831317,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9yMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=7d498ea9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n而家美帝要求強国簽左第二階段先撤關稅<br />\n所以強国一定要被迫情況下同美帝簽協議<br />\n香港要搭順風車<br />\n<br />\n另外, 所羅門聯署:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fbeijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9yMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=ac48bd94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-win